snippet.title: Amber Heard And Elon Musk Take Their Relationship Public
snippet.description:
In late 2016, billionaire Elon Musk and actress Amber Heard were romantically linked for the first time. The relationship first hit the gossip pages just a few months after Musk filed for divorce from ex-wife Talulah Riley, whom he was married to and divorced from twice. Now, the two have taken their romance public. The actress and the tech Amber and Elon came out publicly as a couple in Australia, where Amber is filming 'Aquaman.' The two walked around Queensland, Australia, on Sunday with their arms around each other. The pair were spotted by the paparazzi. Later, the couple posted pictures from an intimate dinner on Musk's instagram page.
